title: The Stepmother
description: Stepmothers have long been associated with bad--even evil--behavior. Which is why young Tera Dice is more than a little suspicious of Dad's hot, new wife(Michelle Lay). When Tera brings her fiancee Alan Stafford home to meet the family, Micheele can't hide her burning attraction to her young, future son-in-law. Will husband Jay Huntington learn of Michelle's secret passion? Or will vengeful housekeeper Ann Marie have a different plan in store? Stephanie Swift costars in a scorching encounter with Johnny Castle, in this tale of seduction,forbidden desires, and passion. Written and directed by Nica Noelle.
